{
  "type": "sectionColumn",
  "id": "section-column-1",
  "width": ["92%", "80%"],
  "height": "100%",
  "align": "center",
  "fill": "#00000080",
  "effects": [{ "type": "backdropBlur", "amount": "24px" }],
  "borderRadius": ["0", "0 0 2rem 2rem"],
  "marginLeft": "0px",
  "marginRight": "0px",
  "marginTop": "0px",
  "marginBottom": "0px",

  "elementOrder": {
    "mobile": ["text-1", "image-1", "text-2"],
    "desktop": ["text-1", "text-2", "image-1"]
  },
  "columns": {
    "mobile": 1,
    "desktop": 3
  },
  "columnWidths": [1, 1, 2],
  "columnGaps": {
    "mobile": "3rem",
    "desktop": "2rem"
  },
  "columnAssignments": {
    "mobile": {
      "text-1": 0,
      "text-2": 0,
      "image-1": 0
    },
    "desktop": {
      "text-1": 0,
      "text-2": 1,
      "image-1": 2
    }
  },
  "definitions": {
    "text-1": {
      "type": "elementRichText",
      "content": "## Rich text demo\n\nParagraph with **bold**, *italic*, and [link](https://example.com). Strikethrough: ~~old text~~. Inline `code` and a snippet:\n\n```\nconst x = 1;\n```\n\n> Blockquote: *nested* and **formatting**.\n\n---\n\n### Lists\n\n- Unordered item one\n- Item two\n\n1. First\n2. Second\n\n### Task list\n\n- [ ] Unchecked\n- [x] Checked\n\n### Table\n\n| A | B |\n| --- | --- |\n| 1 | 2 |\n\nAutolink: https://example.com",
      "variant": "large-regular",
      "align": "left",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "height": "hug",
      "width": "100%",
      "wordWrap": true
    },
    "text-2": {
      "type": "elementBody",
      "text": "This is the second text column. It demonstrates how multiple text elements can be arranged side-by-side on desktop while stacking on mobile.",
      "variant": "large-regular",
      "align": ["left", "center"],
      "textAlign": ["left", "center"],
      "height": "hug",
      "width": "100%",
      "wordWrap": true
    },
    "image-1": {
      "type": "elementImage",
      "src": "EL_LENERO_PREVIEW.webp",
      "alt": "El Lenero preview image",
      "objectFit": "cover",
      "objectPosition": "50% 50%",
      "height": "100%",
      "constraints": [{ "minHeight": "min(400px, 40vh)" }, {}],
      "align": "center"
    }
  }
}
